    modified_response: "I have completed the UI prototype for the AI Spam Shield application, presented as a highly-polished mobile experience within a browser mockup frame.\n\n*   **Cyber Security Identity**: Designed a custom \"Premium Cyber\" theme utilizing deep slate tones alongside brilliant neon-blue accents, paired with \"Space Grotesk\" display typography to convey an authoritative, cutting-edge aesthetic.\n*   **AI Intelligence Dashboard**: Engineered an interactive dashboard featuring a continuous real-time protection animated loop, dynamic AI latency statistics, and highlighted critical threat interceptions.\n*   **Intercept Log Modules**: Created realistic stream logs for both calls and SMS, detailing confidence scores, distinct dynamic threat levels, and generative AI situational analysis.\n*   **Settings & Rules Interface**: Built a configuration screen for toggling aggressive real-time filtering, local on-device heuristics, and silent robocall blocking parameters."
